{"type": "article", "id": 19611, "title": "带花瓣的家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142128ipINTKFsf7VM0xJy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦的设计师 Marcin Rusak 将花瓣放在树脂里凝固，然后切割成细条，做成了这种材料。花瓣像是凝固在黑色的背景里，依然保持着绽放的样子，有古典静物油画的冷艳美感。他用这种材料制作了灯、桌子、屏风等物品，它们的形态都很简单，依靠这种材料成为其中优雅的装饰。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142126H9mF3a7IXfCbx02l.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29273504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142126U2LyB0gj9zqRVaEF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142127BfLb5Yps6q7a3GIO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.43525741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142127x5E4HaXJuZ8m1gA9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}